nodes.text: A green-skinned alien was among a group of bounty hunters led by Bossk, Zuckuss, and 4-LOM that tried to steal the carbonite-frozen Han Solo from Boba Fett in 3.5 ABY. The four-armed alien, along with an unnamed Herglic hunter, and Zuckuss, boarded Fett's starship, Slave I. After tricking Furlag, who was charged with securing Fett within his own prisoner cells, Fett dropped down from a hatch and dispatched two of his assailants, blasting and killing the alien and the Herglic.
